{{>header}}
<!-- StyleSheets -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
<title>HungerFree</title>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- this is navbar -->
  {{>navbar}}

  <section class="first-section" style="background-color: black;">

    <div class="jumbotron" id="front_img">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>
          Together,
          <br />
          we can
          <br />
          feed
          <br />
          everyone! 
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <section class="counting_no_section">
      <div class="andr">
      <div class="counter-container">
        <div class="counter">
          <b data-target="316" class="count">0</b> M +
          <h6>Tonnes of food is produced in India</h6>
        </div>

        <div class="counter">
          <b data-target="126" class="count">0</b> M +
          <h6>Tonnes of food is wasted in India</h6>
        </div>

        <div class="counter">
          <b data-target="190" class="count">0</b> M +
          <h6>Indian population remains malnutritioned</h6>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    </section>


  </section>
  <!-- collage-->

  <div class="coll">
   
    <img src="img/coll.png" />
    
    <p >
      Every ninth person in the world is hungry,
      according to the World Food Programme. A staggering 800 Million People
      in the world go to the bed hungry every day, based on an estimated world
      population of 7.6 Billion.
    </p>

  </div>


  <section class="wasting-food">
    <div class="wasting-food-div wasting-food">
      <img src="img/wasting-food-img.png" alt="wasting food img" />
      <h2>
        However, for people who are not even able to eat one meal a day, often
        wonder if all the food that is being wasted around them on a daily basis
        could have filled their stomach.
      </h2>
    </div>
  </section>



  <section class="quote">
    <p>"We know that a peaceful world cannot exist one-third rich and two-thirds hungry."</p>
  </section>



  <section id="share-food" class="sharing">
    <img src="img/sharing-img.png" alt="sharing food" />

    <h2><strong>Share Food</strong></h2>
    <p>
        Why is it that some people have so much
        food that it goes to waste, and why is it that
        some people have to go to bed without even
        being able to have a meal per day? It's high time
        when we start thinking about those unpriviledged people and help them.
    </p>

  </section>

  

